:R-HSA-8857538  a           owl:NamedIndividual , obo:GO_0008150 ;
        rdfs:comment        "HBEGF-stimulated formation of EGFR heterodimers with GPNMB triggers PTK6-mediated phosphorylation and stabilization of the hypoxia inducible factor 1 alpha (HIF1A) under normoxic conditions. This process depends on the presence of a long non-coding RNA LINC01139 (LINK-A) (Lin et al. 2016)." ;
        rdfs:label          "PTK6 promotes HIF1A stabilization" ;
